      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Khalid, from his father, from Abdullah Bin Al Mugheira, from Muawiya Bin Ammar, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The reconciler is not a liar (even if he does lie)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "19. A number of our people have narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Khalid from his father from ‘Abd Allah ibn Mughirah from Mu’awiyah ibn ‘Ammar from abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) has said, ‘A reformer (a peace maker) is not a liar.’” "
        ]
      }
